node.text: Crazy scene offshore Nantucket the last few days…. Tons of whales, tunas, sharks, bait, everything… love it 💥 #nantucket #ack #whales

node.text: Wild day, got into a 500+ pound tuna… @mattkellymercer at the helm 💥 #tuna #nantucket #crazy

node.text: Wild week on Nantucket… the beach shark scene is the best I’ve ever seen, bluefin tuna are thick offshore, giant stingrays and other big sharks are here. Caught over 40 beach sharks from the beach last week 💥 #sharktagging #catchandrelease #tagandrelease #nantucket #ack #tuna #sharks #rays

node.text: First shark of the summer… followed by about 10 more. Nantucket is awesome, beach shark bite is on fire, great to be back. Offshore tunas are chewing as well. Hit me up if you want to get out 💥 #ack #sharktagging #tuna

node.text: I’ve always enjoyed spearfishing, but started going deeper and chasing bigger fish over the last year or so. Freediving may be the most physically and mentally intense form of fishing... dealing with riled up sharks chasing you and your fish definitely takes a while to get used to. The permit in the first slide was shot offshore and was close to the world record (47 lbs) rushed in to get a weight, then took some spearo pics at the beach. Awesome sport, great season 💥 #spearfishing @spearchannel @riffe_international
